flowchart TB
    Frontend[Client Apps\nReact Web / Mobile UI]
    Gateway[API Gateway\nOcelot / YARP]
    Auth[Auth Service]
    Application[Application Service]
    Admin[Admin Service]
    Document[Document Service]
    RabbitMQ[(RabbitMQ Event Bus)]
    AuthDb[(Auth DB)]
    ApplicationDb[(Application DB)]
    AdminDb[(Admin DB)]
    DocumentDb[(Document DB)]
    FileStore[(File Storage\n/app/uploads)]

    Frontend -->|HTTP REST| Gateway
    Gateway -->|Auth routes| Auth
    Gateway -->|Application routes| Application
    Gateway -->|Admin routes| Admin
    Gateway -->|Document routes| Document

    Auth -->|EF Core| AuthDb
    Application -->|EF Core| ApplicationDb
    Admin -->|EF Core| AdminDb
    Document -->|EF Core| DocumentDb
    Document -->|Save files| FileStore

    Auth -->|JWT login / token issuing| Frontend

    Application <-->|application.submitted\napplication.status.changed| RabbitMQ
    Document <-->|document.status.updated| RabbitMQ
    Admin <-->|admin.decision.created| RabbitMQ

    RabbitMQ -->|Consumes document.status.updated\nand admin.decision.created| Application
    RabbitMQ -->|Consumes application.submitted| Admin
    RabbitMQ -->|Consumes application.submitted\nfor checklist / review context| Document
